{"body": "> \t `xdg-open` for only linux|cygwin\r\n\r\nSorry, this comment is incorrect.\r\nI changed code to use `xdg-open` for linux and `cygstart` for cygwin\r\n\r\n\r\n```ruby\r\n...\r\n      case host_os\r\n      ...\r\n      when /linux/\r\n        `xdg-open #{url}`\r\n      when /cygwin/\r\n        `cygstart #{url}`\r\n      else\r\n        puts \"I don't know how to open your default browser...\"\r\n      end\r\n...\r\n```", "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/comments/14032308", "created_at": "2013-02-25T09:32:30Z", "html_url": "https://github.com/rails/rails/pull/9396#issuecomment-14032308", "updated_at": "2013-02-25T09:32:30Z", "repo": "rails", "issue_id": 9396, "user": {"following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/fukayatsu/following{/other_user}", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/fukayatsu/events{/privacy}", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/fukayatsu/orgs", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/fukayatsu", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/fukayatsu/gists{/gist_id}", "html_url": "https://github.com/fukayatsu", "subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/fukayatsu/subscriptions", "avatar_url": "https://0.gravatar.com/avatar/ffdf2b0baba2980a90923978cf32a6ca?d=https%3A%2F%2Fidenticons.github.com%2Fc1ead9d7e9146fba05d5346100cae174.png", "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/fukayatsu/repos", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/fukayatsu/received_events", "gravatar_id": "ffdf2b0baba2980a90923978cf32a6ca", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/fukayatsu/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "login": "fukayatsu", "type": "User", "id": 1041857, "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/fukayatsu/followers"}, "owner": "rails", "_id": {"$oid": "5237ea4ebd3543c1510099a5"}, "id": 14032308, "issue_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/9396"}
